stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_submit: user submits tx with gasLimit
    q_submit --> q_validate: read tx.gasLimit
    q_validate --> q_reject_pool: tx.gasLimit > 16777216
    q_validate --> q_pool: tx.gasLimit <= 16777216
    q_reject_pool --> [*]: return error MAX_GAS_LIMIT_EXCEEDED
    q_pool --> q_pending: tx added to txpool
    q_pending --> q_block_check: tx included in candidate block
    q_block_check --> q_reject_block: block-level gasLimit re-check fails
    q_block_check --> q_execute: block-level gasLimit re-check passes
    q_reject_block --> [*]: block rejected as invalid
    q_execute --> [*]: tx executed within block
